      <div class="job-areas">
        <div class="section">
          <h3>Retail Stores</h3>
          <p>Engage directly with customers, create enriching in-store experiences, and share our passion for fitness and wellness.</p>
          <a href="/careers/retail" class="learn-more">Search for Open Positions</a>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
          <h3>Distribution Centres</h3>
          <p>Be part of the core operations team ensuring timely delivery of products worldwide, crucial for our ongoing success.</p>
          <a href="/careers/distribution" class="learn-more">Search for Open Positions</a>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
          <h3>Guest Education Centres</h3>
          <p>Join our customer service teams to enhance guest experiences through personalized support and education.</p>
          <a href="/careers/education" class="learn-more">Search for Open Positions</a>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
          <h3>Store Support Centres</h3>
          <p>Support our retail environments from behind the scenes in roles spanning Product, Brand, Technology, and more.</p>
          <a href="/careers/support" class="learn-more">Search for Open Positions</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script src="{{ 'main.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>
